## Auth single-token caveat (informational, not urgent)

- [ ] **Split `email_verification_token` into two purposes.** Currently both signup-verification and password-reset reuse the same `User.email_verification_token` field. A pending email-verification gets invalidated when the user requests a password reset (and vice versa). If this bites users, add a separate `password_reset_token` / `_expiry` pair and update `ForgotPasswordSerializer` + `ResetPasswordConfirmSerializer` accordingly.
